This collaborative group was started by Steve GeromeWyatt, and is more formally known as Jesse Newberry Group; Homeless, American Indians, Gays & Lesbians, and Students Party of Davis and middle California. It deals with the interconnected struggles of the Homeless, American Indians, Gays & Lesbians, and Students. By forming a coalition there is more strength. The group will be featured on an episode of Neoism on Friday, October 19.
